'''Miguel João de Andrade Hurst''' (yavutse ku ya 6 Kamena 1967), uzwi cyane nka '''Miguel Hurst''', ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Angola]] akaba n'umuyobozi wa filimi ukomoka mu [[Abadage|Budage]] no muri Porutugali.  Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime''Foreign Land'', ''Le pacte du Silence'' and ''Filhos do Vento''

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 6 Kamena 1967 i Freiburgo mu [[Budage]] arahakurira kugeza ku myaka icyenda. Kuva mu 1977 kugeza 1979, yabaga muri [[Gineya-Biso|Gineya Bissau]] hanyuma yimukira i Lisbonne, [[Porutugali]] kuva 1979 kugeza 2003.  Muri kiriya gihe, yize mu ishuri rya Theatre na Sinema rya Lisbonne nyuma ashinga itsinda ry’imikino rya Pau Preto i Lisbonne. Mu 2003, yimukiye i Luanda, muri Angola maze agirwa umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Angola Institute of Audiovisual and Multimedia Cinema (IACAM). 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1995 yinjiye mu bakinnyi ba ''Teatro Nacional D.Maria II-Lisboa'' . Mu 2007, yakoze nk'umwarimu muri disipuline Intangiriro yubuhanzi muri Universidade Independente, Luanda. Hanyuma guhera mu 2005, yakoraga ku mateka yikinamico mu kigo cyigihugu gishinzwe amahugurwa yubuhanzi umwaka umwe. 

Hagati ya 2010 na 2016, akora muri Goethe-Institut Angola (Instituto Cultural Alemao), aho yaje gusaba umushinga Christiane Schulte umushinga wo kwerekana umuco wa sinema wa [[Angola]].  Yabaye umuyobozi wubuhanzi muri Semba Comunicação, akina kuri televiziyo ''Fora de Série'' .  Nyuma yaje gukorana na opera nyinshi nka ''Sede de Viver'', ''O Comba'', ''O Testamento'' na ''Minha Terra Minha Mãe'' . Hagati aho, mu 2015, yasohoye igitabo cyitwa ''Angola Cinemas'', ku bufatanye n’umufotozi Walter Fernandes. 

Nkuwashinze, umuyobozi nuyobora ibicuruzwa bya Pau Preto Theatre Group, atunganya amakinamico menshi arimo; ''Os Condenados'', ''Museu do Pau Preto'', ''Cabral'', ''Alimária'', ''Idéia Karapinha'', Quem, ''Inyenzi yo'' ''Kuririmba'' na ''Woza Albert'' . 

